snippet.title: Among Us 15 Player Lobbies – Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2021 – Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey Crewmates! Among Us celebrates its 3rd birthday on June 15, and our gift to you is a special update: You can play with EVEN MORE of your friends with the launch of 15 Player Lobbies! 

https://www.microsoft.com/p/among-us/

The 15 Player Lobby update will be launched on all available platforms, including Windows Store and Xbox Game Pass for PC. It will also be available on Xbox consoles later this year.
Among Us is coming to Xbox Game Pass on Xbox consoles & cloud later this year.
